Package bto.Data

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ApplicationDao
    Data Access Object (DAO) interface for managing application-related operations.
    EnquiryDao
    Data Access Object (DAO) interface for managing enquiry-related operations.
    ProjectDao
    Data Access Object (DAO) interface for managing project-related operations.
    UserDao
    Data Access Object (DAO) interface for managing user-related operations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationCSVDao
    Implementation of the ApplicationDao interface for managing applications using a CSV file as the data source.
    EnquiryCSVDao
    Implementation of the EnquiryDao interface for managing enquiries using a CSV file as the data source.
    ProjectCSVDao
    Implementation of the ProjectDao interface for managing projects using a CSV file as the data source.
    UserCSVDao
    Implementation of the UserDao interface for managing user data using CSV files.
